Interface IndexedIntContainer

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayIndexedIntList, ArrayOpenHashIndexedIntSet, BlockIndexedIntList, BlockOpenHashIndexedIntSet, ConstIndexedIntList, SparseIndexedIntList, SyncIndexedIntList
public interface IndexedIntContainer
extends IndexedContainer<java.lang.Integer>, IntIterable, IntVisitable, IndexedIntVisitable

A modifiable container that associates a long index to each element.

This container stores ints, that are mapped to a unique index through which they can be retrieved. An Index over those indexes, and several IntIterable.IntIterators allow access to all the elements of the collection.
